    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>ginger paste</strong> and <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic paste</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
