    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> black beluga lentils</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook for a further 3-4 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
