          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the lentils are cooking, cut your <strong>cucumber[s]</strong> into quarters lengthways, then chop finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>baby plum tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Strip your<strong> mint leaves </strong>from their stems, discard the stems</p><p>Chop the <strong>mint leaves</strong> and <strong>coriander </strong>(including the stalks!)<strong> </strong>together roughly</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
